  "mainHtml": "<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<nav class=\"flex text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">\n<ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">首页</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">chevron_right</span></li>\n<li class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">营销页面管理</li>\n</ol>\n</nav>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row xl:items-end xl:justify-between gap-4\">\n<div>\n<h1 class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface m-0\">营销页面管理</h1>\n<p class=\"text-body-md font-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">统一管理官网页、行业专题页、活动落地页、多语言版本与 SEO / GEO / AI 体验内容发布。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">add_circle</span>新建营销页面</button>\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">publish</span>发布排期</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">web</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary bg-primary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">在线 24</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">已上线页面</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">24</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">覆盖官网首页、询价页、供应商招募页、行业专题与活动页。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">language</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-secondary bg-secondary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">中英双语</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">多语言覆盖</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">18</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">18 个页面已同步中文与英文版本，方便营销投放与海外访问。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">person_search</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-tertiary bg-tertiary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">本周 +56</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">表单转化线索</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">326</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">AI报价入口、供应商招募表单与 Demo 预约是主要转化来源。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">experiment</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-error-container bg-error-container px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">测试中 7</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">A/B 实验</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">7</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">标题、CTA、首屏模型展示与行业文案正在并行测试。</p></div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-5\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">页面矩阵</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">按场景管理官网主页面、活动页和行业专题页的发布状态与目标。</p></div><button class=\"px-3 h-9 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest text-body-md text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\">查看全部页面</button></div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">官网首页</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-label-sm\">已上线</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">承接品牌介绍、AI体验入口与核心能力展示。</div><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>SEO评分</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">91</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>本周UV</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">12,840</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>转化目标</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">提交询价</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">访客智能报价页</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-label-sm\">A/B 测试</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">聚焦模型上传、快速报价与新客转化。</div><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>转化率</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">14.8%</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>主CTA</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">开始智能报价</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>测试变量</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">首屏文案</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">供应商招募页</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-label-sm\">待审核</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">用于承接机加工、钣金、表处等供应商入驻申请。</div><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>待审内容</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">能力对比模块</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>表单完成率</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">63%</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>负责人</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">平台运营</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">行业专题页</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface text-label-sm\">持续更新</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">面向机器人、医疗、新能源等行业输出案例与工艺能力。</div><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>专题数量</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">9</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>AI摘要启用</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">6 页</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>外链增长</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">+22%</span></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-5 space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">发布流程</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">让内容、设计、运营与法务在同一流程里协同上线。</p></div><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-label-sm font-label-sm\">本周排期 5</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">edit_square</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">草稿编辑</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">支持中文、英文、SEO标题、Meta描述与 AI 摘要同步维护。</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">approval</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">审核通过</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">设计规范、品牌文案、法务声明和表单字段统一校验。</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">publish</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">定时发布</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">支持活动页定时上线下线、灰度发布和 A/B 流量分配。</div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">SEO / GEO / AI 内容策略</h3><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">近 7 天</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>搜索词覆盖率</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">78%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[78%] bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>GEO 场景命中率</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">64%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[64%] bg-secondary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-body-md mb-1\"><span>AI 摘要引用率</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">41%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[41%] bg-tertiary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">建议优先补强“CNC加工报价”“AI机械加工平台”“供应商入驻”三类核心页面的结构化问答。</div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div><section class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden mb-8\"><div class=\"p-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-3 bg-surface-bright\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-sur